static String getStoryTemplate(int genreIndex, int storyIndex,
                               String hero, String companion, String weapon,
                               String villain, String power, String creature,
                               String place, String relic, String number) {

    String[][] stories = new String[15][];

    // GENRE 1: Heroic Fantasy
    stories[0] = new String[]{
            // 1. Quest for the Crystal Peaks
            String.format(
                    "%s ventured through %s with %s at their side, gripping %s as the wind howled around them. " +
                            "Every step drew them closer to %s and a raging %s that had frozen the land in fear. " +
                            "By calling on the hidden power of %s again and again, they finally endured %s brutal trials and recovered %s, giving their world a fragile new hope.",
                    hero, place, companion, weapon, villain, creature, power, number, relic
            ),

            // 2. Dragonsoul Reborn
            String.format(
                    "%s and %s journeyed toward %s, following half-burned maps and stories whispered around dying campfires. " +
                            "There they confronted %s and a wild %s whose roar shook the sky, forcing them to wield %s with every ounce of courage they had left. " +
                            "After %s exhausting days locked in struggle, they reclaimed %s and felt the ancient dragonsoul stir awake within it.",
                    hero, companion, place, villain, creature, power, number, relic
            ),

            // 3. Forest of Whispering Bones
            String.format(
                    "Guided by %s, %s stepped into the haunted depths of %s where every tree seemed to lean in and listen. " +
                            "They faced %s and a relentless %s, using %s to cut through both illusion and terror as the forest tried to swallow them whole. " +
                            "Only after %s long nights did they finally secure %s and quiet the whispers that had plagued the living for generations.",
                    companion, hero, place, villain, creature, power, number, relic
            ),

            // 4. The Cursed Crown
            String.format(
                    "%s left %s with %s slung across their back and %s marching beside them, determined to end the age of shadows. " +
                            "Together they confronted %s and a summoned %s that guarded the throne room like a living curse, channeling %s with desperate precision. " +
                            "After surviving %s relentless challenges, they restored %s and shattered the dark legacy that plagued the old crown.",
                    hero, place, weapon, companion, villain, creature, power, number, relic
            ),

            // âœ… FIXED - Exactly 8 %s, 8 arguments
            String.format(
                    "%s traveled with %s to %s, where thunder never stopped rumbling over the jagged cliffs. " +
                            "There they battled %s and %s itself, a towering creature that seemed carved from lightning, forcing them to shape %s into a shield against the storm. " +
                            "Only after %s ferocious battles did they retrieve %s and prove themselves worthy of the stormhammer's legacy.",
